agenda.description: SENATE NOTICE OF PUBLIC HEARING COMMITTEE: Natural Resources & Economic Development TIME & DATE: 9:00 AM, Wednesday, February 20, 2019 PLACE: E1.012 (Hearing Room) CHAIR: Senator Brian Birdwell The Senate Committee on Natural Resources and Economic Development will adopt committee rules and hear invited testimony from the Railroad Commission of Texas, the Texas Commission on Environmental Quality, and the Texas Workforce Commission.
